BLOCK - Can be reused. describes its purpose. (what is it? menu or button)
ELEMENT - dependent on the block. describes its purpose (what is this? item, text)
MODIFIER - defines the appearance, state, or behavior of a block or element.


Block or element?

pag reusable - block
pag di reusable/nakadepend lang sa ibang component - element

